metadata.name: ENS EMOJI PUNK - NICK.ETH
metadata.description:
Nick Johnson, AKA "Nick.eth" is the founder and lead developer of the "Ethereum Name Service" - https://app.ens.domains

Soon after I got introduced to ENS back in 2021, I realised that there was so much more utility hidden below the surface layer of what this Web3 Protocol offers. 

Using my curiosity and love of Art, Tech and Blockchain development, I naturally wanted to test the extremes of what was possible...

This Artwork is a 1of1 NFT, a result of many many hours experimenting with using Emojis to formulate ENS (.eth) Domain combinations, that when displayed on the correct screen size/format produce this new and revolutionary artistic style.

My plan is to continue exploring the possibilities within this new dimension of Web3 Art. I hope you will enjoy this journey with me into the Metaverse!

However, the question still remains - Is this Art or a Domain ?
